@startuml pd-architecture
title Disaggregated Prefill/Decode — Request Flow

participant Client #LightGreen
participant "agentgateway\n(Envoy)" as GW #LightBlue
participant "EPP\n(Endpoint Picker)" as EPP #LightBlue
participant "vLLM Prefill\nT4 · dagobah" as P #Plum
participant "vLLM Decode\nRTX 3060 · endor" as D #Gold

Client -> GW: request
GW -> EPP: ext-proc: pick pod
EPP -> P: 1. prefill (process prompt)

P -> P: build KV cache

P -[#Red]> D: <b>RDMA / NIXL</b>\n25GbE ConnectX-4 · ~19.5ms
note right: KV cache transfer\nGPU-to-GPU zero-copy

EPP -> D: 2. decode (generate tokens)
D -> D: FlashInfer attention\non transferred KV cache

D --> Client: stream tokens · 96.8 tok/s peak

@enduml
